# Vercel only serves the WebPreview static site (see vercel.json rewrites).
# Patterns are ROOT-ANCHORED with a leading slash so they can never match a
# nested path such as WebPreview/assets/ (Vercel ignore matching is
# case-insensitive, so an unanchored "Assets" would wrongly drop "assets").
/Assets
/Packages
/ProjectSettings
/UserSettings
/UnityInstallRepair
/Library
/Temp
/Logs
/.github
/*.md
/*.cmd
/*.ps1
/*.url
